Oftentimes, just talking to another person will

65
00:03:44,697 --> 00:03:46,817
help you work out your errors.

66
00:03:46,817 --> 00:03:48,097
Don't be afraid to ask for help.

67
00:03:48,097 --> 00:03:51,559
There's a lot of really nice Android developers out in the community who

68
00:03:51,559 --> 00:03:53,880
are willing to help you.

69
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:58,200
In fact, being able to ask for help is an important skill for developers.

70
